1. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 27, for the Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).
2. The Schedule renumbered as the Schedule ( 1 ) thereof by Act 3 of 1989, s. 94 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).
